    "testimonials_pwJjb6": {
      "type": "testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "testimonial_gtTMKH": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>I don’t usually leave reviews, but this was worth it. The trousers I ordered fit beautifully and are incredibly comfortable around the waist, which is important to me. They look polished without feeling stiff. I’ve already worn them several times and they still look brand new.</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/zakrywajacy_brzuch_12.jpg",
            "author": "Linda A.",
            "author_info": "Calgary, AB"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_xV3a7d": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "4-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>I had a small question about sizing before placing my order and received a helpful reply within a day. That gave me confidence to go ahead. The sweater I chose fits exactly as described and feels substantial, not thin or flimsy. Very happy with the overall experience.</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/zakrywajacy_brzuch_14.jpg",
            "author": "Carol M.",
            "author_info": "Vancouver, BC"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_h9QNci": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "4-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>The photos online are very true to life. The color I received matched perfectly and the fabric has a lovely weight to it. You can tell care goes into selecting the pieces. It feels like a boutique that values quality over trends.</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/zakrywajacy_brzuch_16.jpg",
            "author": "Deborah T.",
            "author_info": "Toronto, ON"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_LXbrX8": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>I absolutely love my new coat from Susan & Lily. The fit is spot on and the quality is even better than I expected. It feels elegant yet so easy to wear. Already had compliments!</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/zakrywajacy_brzuch_13.jpg",
            "author": "Margaret C.",
            "author_info": "Halifax, NS"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_VrGpB8": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "4-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>I’m quite particular about stitching and finishing, and I was impressed. No loose threads, seams are neat, and the garment hangs beautifully. It arrived well packaged and in excellent condition. I’ll definitely browse again.</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/zakrywajacy_brzuch_15.jpg",
            "author": "Barbara W.",
            "author_info": "Ottawa, ON"
          }
        }
      },
